          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A windowless He-4 gas target.  The thickness of the",
                "extended  windowless He gas target was determined using",
                "the 4-He(7-Li,gamma)11-B reaction at E/lab = 1.668 MeV,",
                "energy loss measurements of different ions, and the",
                "4-He(7-Li,4-He)7-Li* reaction at E/lab = 3.325 MeV.",
                "The weighted average of the results yields N(4-He) =",
                " (4.21+/-0.14)E+17 atoms/cm2 with an effective target",
                "length of 42.6+/-1.4 mm, that corresponds to an energy",
                "loss for the 12-C ions smaller than 25 KeV in the",
                "investigated energy range."
              ]
            }
          ],
